==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Evanid
<hw>E*van"id</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>evanidus</ets>, fr. <ets>evanescere</ets>. See
<er>Evanesce</er>.]</ety> <def>Liable to vanish or disappear; faint;
weak; evanescent; <as>as, <ex>evanid</ex> color</as>.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>They are very transitory and <qex>evanid</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Barrow.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Evanish</ent>⟦br⟧
